TITLE: Configuring Shopify API Settings in Nuxt Config
DESCRIPTION: Configuration example for setting up Shopify API credentials in nuxt.config.ts, including storefront and admin API settings.
SOURCE: https://github.com/konkonam/nuxt-shopify/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
export default defineNuxtConfig({
    shopify: {
        name: 'quickstart-abcd1234',
        clients: {
            storefront: {
                apiVersion: '2024-10',
                publicAccessToken: 'YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN',
            },

            admin: {
                apiVersion: '2024-10',
                accessToken: 'YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN',
            },
        },
    },
})
```

