TITLE: Querying Shopify Storefront API with TypeScript in Nuxt
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the automatically typed Shopify Storefront API in a Nuxt server API route. The example shows a GraphQL query for fetching menu and product data with automatic type inference.
SOURCE: https://github.com/konkonam/nuxt-shopify/blob/main/docs/configuration/codegen.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
// ~/server/api/example.ts

// ...
const storefront = useStorefront()

const myQuery = await storefront.request(`#graphql
    query ExampleQuery {
        menu(handle: "main-menu") {
            ...MenuFields
        }
        products(first: 10) {
            ...ProductFields
        }
    }
`)
// ...
```

