TITLE: Creating GraphQL Configuration File for IDE Support
DESCRIPTION: YAML configuration that defines GraphQL schema paths to enable IDE support for GraphQL operations in a Nuxt Shopify project.
SOURCE: https://github.com/konkonam/nuxt-shopify/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
